    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: <span id="date"></span></p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly to us when you create an account, such as your name, email address, and social media account credentials required for the scheduling service.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect to operate, maintain, and improve the functionalities of the Postiz app, specifically to authenticate with third-party platforms (like TikTok) to publish your content.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our app integrates with third-party services (e.g., TikTok, Instagram). These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.</p>

    <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <strong>support@example.com</strong></p>

